Privacy Policy
High quality games for iPhone, iPad, iPod Touch, Android, Windows Phone and Blackberry
Privacy Policy
Introduction
PlayCreek has been creating cool games for years. We respect You, our users, and we are dedicated to protecting Your privacy rights. This Privacy Policy applies to all information that You provide to PlayCreek LLC ("
We
", "
Us
" or "
Our
"). This Privacy Policy ("
Privacy Policy
") is created to inform you how we collect, use, store and, in certain cases, share the information you provide us in connection with any Game created by Us (the "
Games
") or with Our Website www.playcreek.com (the "
Website
") or any game services provided by PlayCreek and accessible through or connected to our Website or Games (all together, the "
Services
").
This Privacy Policy only applies to any Personal Information (which will be defined below) obtained from Your use of Our Website or Our Services. This Privacy Policy does not apply to any information that You may provide to third parties as described below. You should contact such third parties directly in order to learn about their Privacy Policies.
We reserve the right to amend this Privacy Policy from time to time without notice. Please check the Privacy Policy regularly.
By using the Services, you agree to the collection and use of your personal information as explained in this Privacy Policy. If You do not agree with the original or later revised Privacy Policy conditions, you should not use our Services. If You believe We do not adhere to this Privacy Policy, please contact Us at
support@playcreek.com
Which Personal Information We collect
"
Personal Information
" is the information about You by which You may be identified. We collect and store certain kind of Personal Information about You only in order to provide our Services to You in a best way.
The Personal Information We may collect and store can include:
-- Your name, Your gender and Your age/date of birth;
-- Your IP Address and Your country;
-- Your e-mail Address.
How We use Your Personal Information
We may use Your Personal Information in order to:
-- respond Your requests and answer Your questions;
-- gather internal statistics and aggregate data for further improving of our Games based on such collected statistics;
-- ensure we comply with any applicable laws and regulations;
-- prevent cheating, fraud or crime (we may need to pass your Information to organizations involved in crime and fraud prevention in cases when such action is reasonably necessary to prevent fraud or crime).
We may ask you to provide us Your e-mail address, which will be used only to send you notifications related to our Services and to respond to your questions. We will not give or sell your e-mail addresses to any third party. We comply with the provisions of any applicable anti-spam laws. We may also store any e-mails sent from You to Us for our reference.
Non-Personal Information that We collect
Every time You play Our Games, the details of Your interaction are collected and retained by Us. Our Services may record game play information such as Your high scores, game session duration, certain details of your interaction with any certain parts of our Games and other.
Third party social networks or platforms
You may allow our Games to interact with a third party social networks or platforms (the "
Networks
"), such as Facebook, which will provide Personal and other Information about You to Us. We may use Your name, profile picture, or other information as the part of our Services interaction with the Networks and display to You or other users as the part of our Services. These Networks are created and maintained by third parties which are not affiliated with PlayCreek. You need to ensure that you read their Terms of Service and Privacy Policies to learn how they treat your Information and what Information they might share with Us.
Third-Party Advertising
We may use third-party advertising networks to display ads in Our Games. We do not provide any Personal Information to third-party advertising companies that may identify You in any way. However, this Privacy Policy does not apply to any information that You may provide to third-party Applications that you access via interacting with the third-party advertisements in Our Games. You should contact such third parties directly in order to learn about their privacy policies in connection with using their Applications.
How we may disclose Your Information
We may share your data with third parties in the following cases:
-- with Your consent (including as set out in this Privacy Policy);
-- when Your Information is not Personal but is aggregated as anonymous, which means that you cannot be identified from such Information;
-- in order to comply with any legal obligation, or to protect the rights, property, or safety of PlayCreek, or Our users;
-- in case of an investigation of fraud, intellectual property infringement, or other illegal activity that may involve Us or You to any kind of legal liability;
-- in order to fulfill our Terms and Conditions and/or any other agreement between Us with You being in force.
Information Security
We have take reasonable technical and other measures in order to protect Your Personal and Non-Personal Information from unauthorized access, use, changing or disclosure, or from accidental loss. However, it is impossible to 100% guarantee that illegal third parties will never manage to overcome those measures or that they will not use Your Personal Information for any improper purpose.
Please keep in mind when sending Us any kind of Personal Information via e-mail or other messaging system, that such messaging systems are not secure and cannot be used to safely transfer such Personal data to Us.
Contacting Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact Us at
support@playcreek.com
This Privacy Policy was last updated on April 7, 2014
